ISLAMABAD, Feb 20 (APP): Caretaker Federal Minister for Information, Broadcasting and Parliamentary Affairs Murtaza Solangi on Tuesday presented in the Senate the State Bank of Pakistan Governor’s Annual Report for the financial year 2022-23.
This report covers the achievement of the Bank’s objectives, the conduct of monetary policy, the state of Pakistan’s economy, and the financial system, under section 9A(2) of the State Bank of Pakistan Act, 1956.
